  <div style=3D"display: none; max-height: 0px; overflow: hidden;">Welcome =
back to Wall Power. Art Basel C.E.O. Noah Horowitz, who had dinner with sev=
eral international gallerists the night before at Joe=E2=80=99s Stone Crab,=
 cited slower sales and longer payment cycles as among the burdens on the g=
alleries leading up to the December fair. But once the convention hall open=
ed on Wednesday, he reported a collective feeling of relief. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=
=80=99s been a long year for our gallery clients.=E2=80=9D
  =20
