=E2=80=99t be somewhere else=E2=80=94I may have ended up with a better read=
 on what=E2=80=99s actually going on in the market. On the one hand, there =
were plenty of reports that the fair had gone well, and that smart, young b=
uyers were giving the market the energy and enthusiasm it needs; on the oth=
er, there was still a sense that the market was directionless and adrift. <=
br/></td>
