          <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Displaying work by =
famous artists like Basquiat and Kusama (the Rubells have two infinity room=
s on the other side of the hallway) is obviously a flex. But showing work b=
y forgotten talent and re-engaging with choices you made decades ago, even =
at the risk of exposing your past mistakes, is what real collectors do=E2=
=80=94never give up on the art.</td>
